Richard Rust https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Rust 0 Richard Rust (July 13, 1938 – November 9, 1994) was an American actor of stage, television, and film born in Boston, probably best remembered for his role as a young lawyer in NBC's Sam Benedict series (1962-1963).
